              },
              {
                "text": "2: 26%",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "text": "3: 72%",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "text": "4: 97%",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "text": "≥5: 100%",
                "children": []
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "text": "Variables:",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "G (Glasgow\\NComa Scale):",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "3-4: +2",
                    "children": []
                  },
                  {
                    "text": "5-12: +1",
                    "children": []
                  },
                  {
                    "text": "13-15: +0",
                    "children": []
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "text": "V (Volumen HIC):",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "≥30 cm3: +1",
                    "children": []
                  },
                  {
                    "text": "<30 cm3: +0",
                    "children": []
                  },
                  {
                    "text": "Calculo: (AxBxC)/2 en cm, donde A es el diámetro mayor de la hemorragia, B el diámetro perpendicular\\Na A y C el número de cortes donde se visualiza la hemorragia multiplicado por el grosor del corte.",
                    "children": []
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "text": "I (Hemorragia\\NIntraventricular):",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Sí: +1",
                    "children": []
                  },
                  {
                    "text": "No: +0",
                    "children": []
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "text": "L (Localización\\NInfratentorial):",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Sí: +1",
                    "children": []
                  },
                  {
                    "text": "No: +0",
                    "children": []
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "text": "E (Edad):",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "≥80 años: +1",
                    "children": []
                  },
                  {
                    "text": "<80 años: +0",
                    "children": []
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
